  &lt;blockquote class=&#34;twitter-tweet&#34; data-dnt=&#34;true&#34;&gt;&lt;p lang=&#34;en&#34; dir=&#34;ltr&#34;&gt;Introducing Imagen, a new text-to-image synthesis model that can generate high-fidelity, photorealistic images from a deep level of language understanding. Learn more and and check out some examples of &lt;a href=&#34;https://twitter.com/hashtag/imagen?src=hash&amp;amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw&#34;&gt;#imagen&lt;/a&gt; at &lt;a href=&#34;https://t.co/RhD6siY6BY&#34;&gt;https://t.co/RhD6siY6BY&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=&#34;https://t.co/C8javVu3iW&#34;&gt;pic.twitter.com/C8javVu3iW&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&amp;mdash; Google AI (@GoogleAI) &lt;a href=&#34;https://twitter.com/GoogleAI/status/1529165219997528064?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw&#34;&gt;May 24, 2022&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

